<div class="enlarge_measure">
    <div class="img_wrap">
        <img data-original="https://media.npr.org/assets/img/2020/03/10/gettyimages-522193104_wide-f2151dc11cc28d84d1d88b3be642a2993214b704-s1200.jpg" alt="Personal finance advice for riding out a dips in the stock market." />
    </div>
